  "title": "Core Concepts of Foundations of Understanding Review Techniques",
  "lessonText": "This section introduces the foundational concepts essential for effective review techniques.",
  "data": {
    "content": "• Review techniques are essential for consolidating knowledge.\n• Understanding different review methods enhances retention.\n• Key techniques include summarization, self-testing, and spaced repetition.\n• Effective reviews should be tailored to individual learning styles.\n• Regular reviews can prevent forgetting and reinforce learning."
